  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A retrospective analysis was performed using data of patients suffering from non-malignant&#xD;
      SBS-IF. They were treated with teduglutide in a multidisciplinary SBS-IF program at a single&#xD;
      university medical center between June 2016 and June 2020.&#xD;
    </textblock>
